snippet.title: Ori and the Will of the Wisps - E3 2017 - 4K Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Xbox One and Windows 10 exclusive. From the creators of the multi-award winning "Ori and the Blind Forest" comes the highly anticipated sequel: "Ori and the Will of the Wisps.”  Embark on an all new adventure to discover the mysteries beyond the forest of Nibel, uncover the hidden truths of those lost, and unravel Ori's true destiny.
 Official teaser trailer for Ori and the Will of the Wisps. Discover more at http://www.xbox.com/games/ori-will-of-the-wisps. Ori and the Will of the Wisps is a 4K UHD, Xbox One X Enhanced, Xbox Play Anywhere title.

Video with Audio Description: https://youtu.be/ozzI098oeDo
